OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,FHSBC has apologised after it took more
OL,7,Fthan #800 from a Jersey man, who
OL,8,Freceived the money following the
OL,9,Fcollapse of the Blue Islands airline.
OL,11,FElliott Allsopp was refunded #866.92
OL,12,Fby HSBC last year after he was forced
OL,13,Fto book last-minute flights after Blue
OL,14,FIslands' liquidation.
OL,16,FElliott had been planning to take his
OL,17,Fson to Cardiff to watch New Zealand
OL,18,Fplay rugby for the first time, and had
OL,19,Foriginally booked early to ensure they
OL,20,Fwould have the flights in time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
