FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781801274
OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,FHowever, when Blue Islands announced
OL,7,Fit would cease trading, he was set to
OL,8,Flose thousands of pounds.
OL,10,F"It was disappointing for everyone,"
OL,11,FElliott told ITV News. "I did feel for
OL,12,Fall the staff, but for me, I was
OL,13,Fthinking there's the flights gone, the
OL,14,Faccommodations gone, the tickets, and
OL,15,Fthe disappointment for all of us -
OL,16,Fespecially our sons."
OL,18,FElliott was able to book new flights
OL,19,Fwith Loganair at the cost of #866.92
OL,20,Fand completed his trip.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781801274
OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,F"Straight away, I paid again", he
OL,7,Fsaid. "The trip was saved."
OL,9,FWhen he returned, he found out via a
OL,10,FFacebook post that he was entitled to
OL,11,Fa refund from his bank. When he went
OL,12,Fto HSBC, they confirmed that it was
OL,13,Fthe case.
OL,15,FThe refund was deposited into
OL,16,FElliott's account in December last
OL,17,Fyear, but on Monday 1 June, the money
OL,18,Fwas taken out again.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781801274
OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,FThe next day, he received a letter
OL,7,Ffrom HSBC, which he described as
OL,8,F"poorly put together, with strange
OL,9,Fjargon and littered with spelling
OL,10,Fmistakes".
OL,12,FIt read that the bank was "unable to
OL,13,Fassist any further" and that "you
OL,14,F(sic) account may go overdrawn and
OL,15,Fincur charges".
OL,17,FElliott said he spent hours on the
OL,18,Fphone with HSBC trying to sort the
OL,19,Fproblem out.
OL,26,@vD@ApmvD@Epn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781801274
OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,F"I was shocked. I couldn't understand
OL,7,Fit - no warning, I really didn't know
OL,8,Fwhat to do," the All Blacks fan
OL,9,Fexplained.
OL,11,F"It's a lot of money, and it said in
OL,12,Fthe letter that if you hadn't had the
OL,13,Ffunds in your account, you would have
OL,14,Fbeen charged for going overdrawn."
OL,16,FHSBC claimed that Elliott had not
OL,17,Ffollowed the proper protocols when
OL,18,Frequesting a refund.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
