FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1781801274
OL,3,CHSBC apology for All Blacks fan after
OL,4,Cremoving flight cancellation refund
OL,6,FAfter being contacted by ITV News,
OL,7,FHSBC refunded the money and apologised
OL,8,Ffor "any confusion and concern this
OL,9,Fhas caused the customer".
OL,11,FIn a statement, HSBC said: "A full
OL,12,Frefund has now been provided, and we
OL,13,Fare urgently reviewing the
OL,14,Fcircumstances and looking into the
OL,15,Ftimeline as a priority, including the
OL,16,Fsequencing of our communications, and
OL,17,Fwe'll ensure the customer receives a
OL,18,Fclear explanation as soon as possible."
OL,26,@zD@gO]
